                <p>
                    <b>1. Manpower costs</b><br/>
                    • No. of project manpower should commensurate with the work packages being handled by the partner. Detailed justification with scope of work by each project manpower to be clearly mentioned indicating their designation/status. Indicate gross annual salary / fellowship and percentage of time devoted on the project in the explanation along with institutional norms, if any.  
                </p>
